import './NewGameForm.scss'
import React from 'react'
export class NewGameForm extends React.Component {

  render () {
    return (
    <form>
      <select>
        <option>Difficulty</option>
        <option>Easy</option>
        <option>Medium</option>
        <option>Hard</option>
      </select>
      <select>
        <option>Category</option>
        <option>mapped Categories</option>
      </select>
      <input type="number">Number of Questions</input>
      <input type="radio" name="question-type">True/False</input>
      <input type="radio" name="question-type">Multiple Choice</input>
      <input placeholder="Room Name"/>
      <button>Host</button>
    </form>
  )
  }
}
